{"tid":1426761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰機艙有監察鏡頭","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:37:57.000Z","uid":257847,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed41307c77d3ff096a329ecab710e49ed6006a6e","tid":1426761,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:44:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/cathay-pacific-onboard-camera/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2Fcathay-pacific-onboard-camera%2Findex.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=9c3fcdbf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2Fcathay-pacific-onboard-camera%2Findex.html&h=1e80f28e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/travel/article/cathay-pacific-onboard-camera/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n(CNN) &mdash; Hong Kong airline Cathay Pacific has revealed it is recording passenger activity on its aircraft via inflight entertainment systems and video cameras, re-opening an uncomfortable debate over surveillance on airplanes.<br />\n<br />\nThe carrier, frequently named among the world's best, outlined its information gathering in an updated privacy policy published at the end of July 2019.<br />\n<br />\nCathay confirmed it is collecting images of passengers while they're on board as well as logging their usage of the in-flight entertainment system (IFE) and how they spend time during the flight.<br />\n<br />\nThe airline says the images are not captured from embedded seat-back cameras.<br />\n<br />\nIn its privacy policy, the airline says the data collection is designed to improve the flying experience with additional personalization. The airline also says data could be shared with third-party partners for marketing purposes.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We will retain your Personal Data for as long as is necessary,&quot; reads the policy."},{"pid":"fd4ff95c8be46839332b1fb79f263a3826127d8c","tid":1426761,"uid":257847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e679ea31d1009d50abdc235c3edbe1a84108ebef","tid":1426761,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"幫手推下呢個post<br />\n<br />\n每個星期三都係成場運動嘅轉捩點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426772</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bef66ca389906a34bd5b3e78132871bac7219e8e","tid":1426761,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正式同中國接軌"},{"pid":"ff65992dab8b540d77aa8c090e529b2f932883ad","tid":1426761,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:52:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d8861f4c9088811a64b8a1bcbc432a36323d33","tid":1426761,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"請廣傳，連登仔就民間記者會公投！！！要大家嘅民意授權，越多人支持，佢地講既野就越有代表性！<br />\n<br />\n一個屬於抗爭者既發聲平台！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.easypolls.net/poll.html?p=5d499813e4b027365670587c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.easypolls.net%2Fpoll.html%3Fp%3D5d499813e4b027365670587c&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2